; Regression test for GitHub issue #1603: Balance assertions broken when
; combined with fixed commodities. A balance assertion/assignment using a
; lot-priced commodity like "= 0 STOCK {$1}" should work without error,
; rather than producing "Subtracting amounts with different commodities".

2000/01/01 A
    Assets  100 STOCK {$1}
    Income

2000/02/01 B
    Assets2
    Assets  = 0 STOCK {$1}

test balance --empty assets
             0 STOCK  Assets
           100 STOCK  Assets2
--------------------
           100 STOCK
end test

test reg assets
00-Jan-01 A                     Assets                    100 STOCK    100 STOCK
00-Feb-01 B                     Assets2                   100 STOCK    200 STOCK
                                Assets                   -100 STOCK    100 STOCK
end test
